---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Luis Leon">
  <section class="page-header container">
    <p class="eyebrow">About Me</p>
    <h1>Electrical engineering through design, testing, and debugging</h1>
  </section>

  <article class="page-content container">
    <p>
      My engineering experience combines FPGA development, embedded
      programming, mixed-signal electronics, PCB validation, and hardware
      troubleshooting.
    </p>

    <p>
      I enjoy working across the complete development process, from defining
      requirements and designing an architecture to implementing, testing,
      measuring, and debugging the finished system.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h2>Core skills</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>SystemVerilog and Verilog</li>
        <li>FPGA design and verification</li>
        <li>Zynq-7000 and AXI4-Lite</li>
        <li>Embedded C and C++</li>
        <li>PCB design and hardware bring-up</li>
        <li>Oscilloscopes and logic analyzers</li>
        <li>Vivado, Vitis, XSim, KiCad, LTspice, and MATLAB</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>